longBusinessSummary: James Maritime Holdings, Inc. manages transport carriers. It transports natural bulk cargo and gas related products, such as condensate, LPG, and LNG to Japan. The company was formerly known as Out-Takes, Inc. and changed its name to James Maritime Holdings, Inc. in February 2015. James Maritime Holdings, Inc. was founded in 1992 and is based in Salt Lake City, Utah.
